<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Welcome to AudioLounge</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: var(--primaryBgColor);
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: var(--secondaryBgColor);
        border-radius: 4px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .header img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
      }

      h1 {
        color: var(--primaryTextColor);
        font-size: 28px;
        margin: 0;
      }

      p {
        color: var(--secondaryTextColor);
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .emoji {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .signature {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--secondaryTextColor);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="<%= imageUrl %>" alt="AudioLounge Banner" />
      </div>
      <h1>Welcome to AudioLounge! <span class="emoji">🎉</span></h1>
      <p>Dear <%= name %> <span class="emoji">👋</span>,</p>
      <p>
        Thank you for joining AudioLounge, the ultimate platform for hosting and participating in captivating audio
        events on a wide range of topics. We are thrilled to have you as part of our community!
        <span class="emoji">🎧🌟</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        At AudioLounge, we believe in the power of conversations and the impact they can have on personal growth and
        collective knowledge. Our mission is to create a vibrant space where individuals from all walks of life can
        connect, converse, and share their thoughts in real-time, fostering meaningful discussions and
        knowledge-sharing. <span class="emoji">🗣️💡</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        With AudioLounge, you can explore a diverse range of audio events, including panel discussions, interviews,
        workshops, and more. Engage with experts, thought leaders, and fellow enthusiasts to expand your horizons, gain
        insights, and build valuable connections. <span class="emoji">🌍🔊</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        We encourage you to explore our platform, discover events that align with your interests, and actively
        participate in the discussions. Your unique perspectives and contributions will enrich the conversations and
        create a dynamic environment for everyone involved. <span class="emoji">🌈💬</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is always here to help. Feel free to reach out to
        us at support@audiolounge.com. <span class="emoji">📧🤝</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        Once again, welcome to AudioLounge! We're excited to embark on this audio journey with you.
        <span class="emoji">🎙️✨</span>
      </p>
      <p class="signature">
        Best regards,<br />
        The AudioLounge Team <span class="emoji">🎧🌟</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
